{"tid":883712,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"有養開龜龜嘅麻煩入一入黎","createTime":"2018-10-31T04:49:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-05T01:21:49.000Z","uid":203499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f02df756ecfce85230fe2fb1be1df47268739058","tid":883712,"uid":203499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T04:49:57.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n我養緊隻巴西紅耳龜<br />\n都大概十歲架喇<br />\n近排餵佢食野<br />\n一倒完啲龜糧落水<br />\n佢一口咬一啖 然後含住幾粒喺口 游走咗<br />\n然後繼續游好似想去第度咁<br />\n<br />\n上網google過都搵唔到解答<br />\n最接近係話佢想生蛋<br />\n我諗係想儲啲食物去隻蛋度？<br />\n但而家仲未見到有蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇試過咁嘅巴打幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔該晒各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f14826d8598906698e8a77efc3a7284856e7bfc9","tid":883712,"uid":64318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T04:51:01.000Z","msg":"無Nancy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db3fe61758873acc9c65431fa3ca9f2c298ce3a4","tid":883712,"uid":203499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f14826d8598906698e8a77efc3a7284856e7bfc9","tid":883712,"uid":64318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T04:51:01.000Z","msg":"無Nancy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T04:58:55.000Z","msg":"即係咩意思？"},{"pid":"6db6dd3ec21a700bc76c22371b21ba67d014ca3f","tid":883712,"uid":90820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db3fe61758873acc9c65431fa3ca9f2c298ce3a4","tid":883712,"uid":203499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f14826d8598906698e8a77efc3a7284856e7bfc9","tid":883712,"uid":64318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T04:51:01.000Z","msg":"無Nancy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T04:58:55.000Z","msg":"即係咩意思？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T13:17:27.000Z","msg":"生蛋唔係咁㗎喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n乜嘢儲啲食物去隻蛋度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家轉天氣啦<br />\n佢之前嗰十年唔過冬㗎咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d37937d9db0352c557cfa787923d76cfb8a7f66d","tid":883712,"uid":81906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T03:43:14.000Z","msg":"可能係塞蛋唔舒服？<br />\n有冇試過餵蝦？佢有冇食欲？"},{"pid":"bfd93b096e853a3ded583305ebae01762dde14fb","tid":883712,"uid":158472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T04:46:07.000Z","msg":"清 啱啱養定養咗十年?<br />\n我隻就十二歲,一日一餐,識得自動波出現r飯食<br />\n而呢幾日就變咗兩日到先一餐(記得12月到開始唔食嘢間唔中飲下水)<br />\n唔知解唔解答到你呢?"},{"pid":"14c32675281407859af8d3a165b34d4f4218fbdc","tid":883712,"uid":71740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T05:31:52.000Z","msg":"我果隻最近呢個禮拜開始唔食野，係咪開始要冬眠啦？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a11dec65d306077ccb7da4fc4c3b8b4141d6f114","tid":883712,"uid":203499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d37937d9db0352c557cfa787923d76cfb8a7f66d","tid":883712,"uid":81906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T03:43:14.000Z","msg":"可能係塞蛋唔舒服？<br />\n有冇試過餵蝦？佢有冇食欲？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T12:10:04.000Z","msg":"冇餵過蝦呀<br />\n我見佢次次都清晒啲糧嘅<br />\n不過係食得奇怪啲姐"},{"pid":"4dc5bb86fbcdb92abf1945c77bb09711c62f24bb","tid":883712,"uid":203499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bfd93b096e853a3ded583305ebae01762dde14fb","tid":883712,"uid":158472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T04:46:07.000Z","msg":"清 啱啱養定養咗十年?<br />\n我隻就十二歲,一日一餐,識得自動波出現r飯食<br />\n而呢幾日就變咗兩日到先一餐(記得12月到開始唔食嘢間唔中飲下水)<br />\n唔知解唔解答到你呢?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T12:10:39.000Z","msg":"養咗十年喇 但冇見過佢咁"},{"pid":"bb33ae969950e10c375b79a274705d0d817001be","tid":883712,"uid":203499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14c32675281407859af8d3a165b34d4f4218fbdc","tid":883712,"uid":71740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T05:31:52.000Z","msg":"我果隻最近呢個禮拜開始唔食野，係咪開始要冬眠啦？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T12:11:58.000Z","msg":"但我睇過好似要好凍先會冬眠<br />\n大概得番幾度咁"},{"pid":"7886d9e291a95b2f2bd68b677bf10623efe391d6","tid":883712,"uid":158472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4dc5bb86fbcdb92abf1945c77bb09711c62f24bb","tid":883712,"uid":203499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bfd93b096e853a3ded583305ebae01762dde14fb","tid":883712,"uid":158472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T04:46:07.000Z","msg":"清 啱啱養定養咗十年?<br />\n我隻就十二歲,一日一餐,識得自動波出現r飯食<br />\n而呢幾日就變咗兩日到先一餐(記得12月到開始唔食嘢間唔中飲下水)<br />\n唔知解唔解答到你呢?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T12:10:39.000Z","msg":"養咗十年喇 但冇見過佢咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T13:22:10.000Z","msg":"據我所知唔關生蛋事(十歲咁快有蛋生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  )<br />\n呢排太陽猛，得閒俾佢曬多d，應該會好d<br />\n亦有可能夜晚溫度低咗，搞到無嘜胃口"},{"pid":"a422df5dee1730f4bdac670a53e942d5da031ef6","tid":883712,"uid":201931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T16:17:59.000Z","msg":"我個隻養左8年，有時都會咁樣，但好似冇分季節，我估佢係見到我望住佢 以為我會搶佢啲野食所以先咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過近排佢有時會踢自己條尾，都幾用力，有冇巴絲知道點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd5a57e37e533cd621c7a01d974f6758644c70fd","tid":883712,"uid":28477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T16:26:29.000Z","msg":"擔心咪睇下獸醫，有病醫病無病身體檢查<br />\n唔好好似之前有個post條撚屌咁乾養左多年養到反晒甲重覺得隻龜咁樣好得意<br />\n（唔係話樓主係D咁既人，純粹想講係養既過程中可能有少少誤解唔清楚導致有D錯養既方法，耐唔耐睇下都唔係壞事）"},{"pid":"933822ea0985f103b0a766211a7b7bb17c4b0c84","tid":883712,"uid":90820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a422df5dee1730f4bdac670a53e942d5da031